    {
      "text": "Third pregnancy (G3P0) confirmed at approximately 5 weeks gestation by positive serum beta-hCG with appropriate 48-hour doubling. 6-week transvaginal ultrasound showed fetal pole with cardiac activity (FHR 112 bpm) and CRL 4.2 mm consistent with 6 weeks 1 day. Pregnancy ended as missed abortion diagnosed 2025-03-10 at 8-week follow-up — absent cardiac activity and growth arrest at 7w1d. D&C performed 2025-03-12."
